      <title>贸易商争夺 Namoi 棉花之际，奥兰·特朗普 (Olam) 击败德雷福斯 (Dreyfus) 出价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/olam-agri-trumps-louis-dreyfus-bid-for-cotton-producer-namoi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奥兰农业控股有限公司（Olam Agri Holdings Ltd.）再次击败了路易达孚公司（Louis Dreyfus Co.）对纳莫伊棉花有限公司（Namoi Cotton Ltd.）的收购，两大农业贸易商争夺这家澳大利亚棉花生产商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/olam-agri-trumps-louis-dreyfus-bid-for-cotton-producer-namoi</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 23:45:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
